statements: SELECT * FROM stock_turnover_reports
SELECT product_id, turnover_rate FROM stock_turnover_reports WHERE product_id = 1
SELECT product_id, turnover_rate FROM stock_turnover_reports WHERE turnover_rate > 0.5
SELECT * FROM stock_turnover_reports ORDER BY turnover_rate DESC
SELECT * FROM stock_turnover_reports WHERE product_id IN (1, 2, 3)
SELECT product_id, turnover_rate FROM stock_turnover_reports WHERE product_id = 100
SELECT * FROM stock_turnover_reports WHERE turnover_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY product_id DESC
SELECT product_id, turnover_rate FROM stock_turnover_reports WHERE turnover_rate < 0.3 AND product_id IN (1, 2, 3) ORDER BY turnover_rate ASC
SELECT product_id, AVG(turnover_rate) AS avg_turnover_rate FROM stock_turnover_reports GROUP BY product_id HAVING avg_turnover_rate > 0.4
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_products, MAX(turnover_rate) AS max_turnover_rate FROM stock_turnover_reports WHERE turnover_rate > 0.2
SELECT * FROM stock_turnover_reports;
SELECT report_id, report_date FROM stock_turnover_reports WHERE report_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT stock_symbol, turnover_rate FROM stock_turnover_reports WHERE turnover_rate > 0.5;
SELECT report_id, report_date, stock_symbol, turnover_rate FROM stock_turnover_reports WHERE stock_symbol = 'AAPL';
SELECT transaction_date, stock_symbol, transaction_type, transaction_amount FROM stock_transactions ORDER BY transaction_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM stock_turnover_reports WHERE report_date > '2021-01-01' AND turnover_rate > 0.1 ORDER BY report_date DESC;
SELECT report_date, stock_symbol, turnover_rate FROM stock_turnover_reports WHERE stock_symbol = 'AAPL' AND report_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT stock_symbol, SUM(transaction_amount) AS total_amount FROM stock_transactions GROUP BY stock_symbol HAVING total_amount > 10000 ORDER BY total_amount DESC;
SELECT report_id, report_date, stock_symbol, turnover_rate FROM stock_turnover_reports WHERE stock_symbol IN ('AAPL', 'GOOGL', 'MSFT') ORDER BY turnover_rate ASC, report_date DESC;

SELECT report_id, report_date, stock_symbol, turnover_rate FROM stock_turnover_reports INNER JOIN stock_transactions ON stock_turnover_reports.stock_symbol = stock_transactions.stock_symbol WHERE turnover_rate < 0.05 AND transaction_type = 'BUY' ORDER BY report_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM StockItems WHERE quantity > 10;
SELECT item_name, purchase_date FROM StockItems ORDER BY purchase_date DESC;

SELECT item_name, quantity FROM StockItems WHERE item_name LIKE 'A%';
SELECT report_date, average_turnover FROM TurnoverRates ORDER BY report_date ASC;
SELECT item_name, quantity, purchase_date FROM StockItems WHERE quantity > 100 ORDER BY purchase_date DESC
SELECT item_name, quantity, purchase_date FROM StockItems WHERE purchase_date > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY quantity ASC
SELECT item_name, quantity, purchase_date FROM StockItems WHERE quantity BETWEEN 50 AND 200 ORDER BY item_name
SELECT sale_id, item_id, sale_date, quantity_sold, total_price FROM Sales WHERE quantity_sold > 10 ORDER BY total_price DESC
SELECT report_date, average_turnover FROM TurnoverRates WHERE report_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' ORDER BY average_turnover ASC
SELECT * FROM stock_reports;
SELECT report_date, stock_symbol, stock_quantity FROM stock_reports WHERE stock_symbol = 'AAPL';
SELECT stock_symbol, stock_quantity, stock_price FROM stock_reports ORDER BY stock_price DESC;
SELECT report_id, stock_symbol, stock_quantity, stock_price FROM stock_reports WHERE stock_quantity > 1000 AND stock_price < 50;
SELECT symbol_id, stock_symbol, company_name FROM stock_symbols ORDER BY company_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM stock_reports WHERE stock_symbol = 'AAPL';
SELECT stock_symbol, stock_quantity FROM stock_reports WHERE stock_quantity > 1000 ORDER BY stock_quantity DESC;
SELECT sr.report_date, sr.stock_symbol, sp.closing_price FROM stock_reports sr JOIN stock_prices sp ON sr.stock_symbol = sp.stock_symbol WHERE sr.report_date = '2022-01-10';

SELECT ss.company_name, sr.report_date, tr.turnover_rate FROM stock_reports sr JOIN stock_symbols ss ON sr.stock_symbol = ss.stock_symbol JOIN turnover_rates tr ON sr.report_id = tr.report_id WHERE tr.turnover_rate > 15 ORDER BY sr.report_date DESC;

SELECT ss.company_name, sr.stock_symbol, sum(sp.volume_traded) AS total_volume_traded FROM stock_reports sr JOIN stock_symbols ss ON sr.stock_symbol = ss.stock_symbol JOIN stock_prices sp ON sr.stock_symbol = sp.stock_symbol GROUP BY sr.stock_symbol, ss.company_name;
SELECT * FROM stocks;
SELECT product_name, quantity FROM stocks WHERE quantity > 10 ORDER BY product_name DESC;
SELECT stock_id, purchase_date FROM purchases WHERE stock_id = 12345;
SELECT sale_id, quantity, sale_date FROM sales WHERE quantity < 5 AND sale_date >= '2023-01-01';
SELECT report_id, report_date, generated_by_user FROM reports WHERE generated_by_user = 'John Doe' ORDER BY report_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM stocks ORDER BY purchase_date DESC, quantity ASC;
SELECT product_name, quantity FROM stocks WHERE quantity > 100 AND sale_date IS NULL;
SELECT stock_id, quantity FROM stocks WHERE purchase_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31';
SELECT stock_id, SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity FROM purchases GROUP BY stock_id HAVING total_quantity > 500;

SELECT reports.report_id, reports.report_date, turnover.turnover_rate FROM reports INNER JOIN turnover ON reports.turnover_id = turnover.turnover_id WHERE turnover.turnover_rate > 0.1 ORDER BY reports.report_date ASC;
